<D>__{and i don't take no mouth from any bartenders neither. there, see? give somebody a rap on the beezer, get some god damn respect around here. now you tell the earps and doc holliday if i see 'em on the street, i'm gonna send 'em all to hell on a shutter. you tell 'em that.}
